T_cells_0= subset(x=merged, idents= c("0" = "0_CD8+ T cells", 
                                      "1" = "1_CD8+ T cells", 
                                      "7" = "7_CD8+ T cells + tumor cells",
                                      "8" = "8_CD4+ T cells"))

2. Normalize and scale the data

# Normalize data
T_cells_0 = NormalizeData(T_cells_0)
T_cells_0 = FindVariableFeatures(T_cells_0, selection.method = "vst", nfeatures = 2000)
T_cells_0 = ScaleData(T_cells_0, vars.to.regress="percent.mt")

# Identify the 10 most highly variable genes
#top10_T_0 = head(VariableFeatures(T_cells_0), 10)

setwd("//asafmadilabfs.tau.ac.il/asafmadilab$/Sarah/experiment/teva/memory/20221225 - memory - scRNA seq/R/3 groups/Figures/T cells/")

3. PCA

# Perform linear dimensional reduction
T_cells_0 = RunPCA(T_cells_0, features = VariableFeatures(object = T_cells_0))

# Examine and visualize PCA results
DimPlot(T_cells_0, reduction = "pca", group.by="Treatment", cols = c("#CFBAE1", "#5C7D9D","#A4DEF9"), pt.size=1.1)

# Determine the ‘dimensionality’ of the dataset
ElbowPlot(T_cells_0, ndims = 40) + theme_classic()

ggsave(file = "Elbow plot_0.png", dpi=300, width=6, height=6)

T_0_intermediate = saveRDS(T_cells_0, file="//asafmadilabfs.tau.ac.il/asafmadilab$/Sarah/experiment/teva/memory/20221225 - memory - scRNA seq/R/3 groups/Objects/Teva_T_0_intermediate_object.rds")

# T cells

11. Finding differentially expressed features (cluster biomarkers)

T_cells.markers = FindAllMarkers(T_cells, only.pos = TRUE, min.pct = 0.25, logfc.threshold = 0.25, return.thresh = 0.05)

Top100Markers_T =
  T_cells.markers %>%
  group_by(cluster) %>%
  top_n(n = 100, wt = avg_log2FC) %>%
  as.data.frame %>% 
  arrange(cluster,-avg_log2FC)

write_csv(Top100Markers_T, "//asafmadilabfs.tau.ac.il/asafmadilab$/Sarah/experiment/teva/memory/20221225 - memory - scRNA seq/R/3 groups/Excels/memory_T cells_DE genes.csv")

T_cells.markers %>%
    group_by(cluster) %>%
    top_n(n = 10, wt = avg_log2FC) -> top10_T
DoHeatmap(T_cells, features = top10_T$gene) + NoLegend() + scale_fill_gradientn(colors = c("blue", "white", "red"))

ggsave(file = "T cells markers - heatmap.png", dpi=300, width=12, height=20)
saveRDS(T_cells, file="//asafmadilabfs.tau.ac.il/asafmadilab$/Sarah/experiment/teva/memory/20221225 - memory - scRNA seq/R/3 groups/Objects/T cells/Teva_T_intermediate_object.rds")
